channel.title: Made a webclient but freezes when logging in
channel.description: Hi I just made the Butterscape client into a web client, I did everything right and it loads properly on the web but when I try to log on it stays in loading screen. It loads properly in some areas but it stays black screen on the majority. I'd highly appreciate it if someone could help me fix this and make it load properly because the client itself seems to be working fine.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: January 10, 2009, 01:28:01 pm[/size][hr]Anyone please help?
